room_title: Escape room "Secrets of the Pharaoh" by MindGames Rock Hill in Rock Hill
room_address: 1807 Cherry Rd Suite #135 Rock Hill, SC 29723
room_description: Professor Carter and his team discovered King Tut in 1922. However, Carter left out some of the details of his discovery. Ever since the artifacts arrived, strange things have been happening. You and your team need to investigate and discover the Secrets of the Pharaoh.  Just a forewarning, there is something going on within his office… the last group vanished…
